About UsBenhamou Global Ventures (BGV) is an early-stage venture capital firm based in Silicon Valley. Like the talented entrepreneurs we work with we share a passion and commitment for building valuable companies; and especially those that drive the digital transformation of enterprises. 
We place particular emphasis on cloud technologies; virtual and software defined networking; productivity-based applications; cyber security, mobility and the Internet of Things. These companies will already have a product or proof of concept validated  by a few customers and seek the expertise of the BGV team to fine tune and scale their marketing and sales plans. Targeted opportunities will tend to exploit three fundamental disruptive shifts:
1.“Extending” the enterprise to a new mobile perimeter of users and “Things”2.“Virtualizing” infrastructure and applications through cloud architectures 
3.“Defending” core assets against cyber threats of all types
 We are a team of people that combine many years of investment experience with successful senior operating roles in major global companies. This has enabled us to establish a powerful network of technical advisors, executives and functional experts who will actively engage with our portfolio companies. Together we are able to offer our entrepreneurs substantial expertise, resources and strong connections. 
“We are often the first and most active institutional investor. Our goal is to partner with our CEO’s to provide the support and advice they need, in order to build game changing companies”
Anik Bose, General Partner
Learn more about our approach to investing









