y in adding the value actually requested by the entrepreneur instead of becoming a lead balloon for the executive team to manage (unlike other venture firms who tout their value add).  For me this translated to a patient and ideal investment partner on all frontsGarret Gafke, CEO Identity MindBGV is a new breed of venture capital , it is the brainchild of serial entrepreneurs and experienced operating individuals that have built and operated great companies. They understand the needs of the entrepreneurs and what it take to build  great technology companiesAmir Nayyerhabibi, Serial EntrepreneurWe’ve found that getting a BGV partner means having several powerhouse operating experts behind you.  With vast knowledge, experience and a formidable network this creates an invaluable “company building” partner.  The entire BGV team cooperates to deliver multi-disciplinary expertise with responsive, pragmatic and constructive adviceBranden Spikes, CEO/Founder – Spikes Security








