^ "the Finance Innovation cluster on the road". AGEFI. 12 July 2007. 
^ "Pricing Partners to leverage grid computing ressources". AGEFI. 26 June 2008. 
^ "Young French company leads the way in financial software innovation". Microsoft. 1 September 2009. 
