^ "Technology vendor rankings 2011: The results". Risk Magazine. 1 April 2011. 
^ "ICBC Asia Moved to Pricing Partners’ Derivatives Pricing Analytics". Asia Trading. May 2011. 
^ "Natixis Taps Pricing Partners for Index Calculation". Waters technology magazine. 12 July 2012. 
^ "Structured Products Technology Rankings 2013". Structured Products Magazine. March 2013. 
^ "Thomson Reuters Acquires OTC Derivatives Pricing Analytics Provider, Pricing Partners". Thomson Reuters. June 2013. 
